summary:
The core of my being is fuelled by curiosity, creativity and research. I pioneer, explore and experiment to gain insights that I want to share with others in order to impact society for the common good. I built my eclectic career in several industries including movie/video productions, journalism, music, market research, and teaching. In all of my positions and projects, investigation, analysis, conceptual thinking, tenacity and solving problems are the connecting skills that I rely on to deliver results that are beyond expectations. I am looking at the big picture and connect the dots. With my multicultural background and having lived and worked in Germany, Israel, United Kingdom, Portugal and the Netherlands, I always quickly adapted to new environments and refined therefore my cultural sensitivity. 
Looking ahead and picking up on trends and developments in society has become second nature. In one of my projects in 2016 I already worked on a product idea powered by AI. As a next step in my career I envision a position, for example, as an (AI) Ethics Consultant or Researcher in (Social) Media or Tech or a role as a Futurist, where I can research and create scenarios for institutes, labs or think thanks.
